  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个博弈论相关的流程图，核心是几种不同的博弈类型。我想先放六个节点：Compliance game、Bailout game、Bargaining game、Coding game、Definition game，还有一个Risk节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，六个博弈类型节点。Risk作为独立节点，它和其他节点的关系是怎样的？还有，我看到您提到了Press和Signal，这两个需要作为节点出现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Press",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Press和Signal不是博弈类型，是中间状态。Risk指向Signal，Signal再指向Bargaining game。另外Place到Press有一条边，但Press暂时不指向其他节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出六个博弈节点，然后加上Risk→Signal→Barg的链条，还有Place→Press的边。方向用从左到右的LR布局可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "LR布局可以。等等，我检查一下——Bargaining game和Bailout game之间是双向的，互相指向。还有Definition game要指向Bargaining game。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Barg↔Bail的双向箭头，还有Define→Barg的边。Coding game和Definition game之间有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Define",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，Coding game指向Definition game，表示编码博弈之后进入定义博弈。另外Compliance game也要指向Definition game。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了Code→Define和Audit→Define的连接。现在六个博弈节点都连上了：Audit和Code都汇入Define，Define再到Barg，Barg和Bail互相循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚才说错了——Risk→Signal→Barg这条链，让我再想想。Signal应该是从Risk出来，但Press那边……Place→Press是独立的，不接入主流程对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Risk→Signal→Barg是主流程的一条分支，Place→Press是另一条独立分支，两者不交汇。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个结构。六个博弈类型形成核心网络，Risk-Signal作为外部输入触发Bargaining，Place-Press是另一条并行的状态路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程图已完成。核心结构：Audit和Code汇入Define，Define到Barg，Barg与Bail双向循环；Risk通过Signal接入Barg；Place到Press独立存在。整体LR布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
